title: Machinarium Collection Edition Patch 2758a-GOG
description: The definitive version of Machinarium is live!Help Josef the robot save his girlfriend Berta kidnapped by the Black Cap Brotherhood gang! Now in full-screen with 12 new achievements, additional languages and full controller support.Machinarium is the award-winning independent adventure game developed by the makers of Samorost and Botanicula.A little robot who been thrown out to the scrap yard behind the city must return and confront the Black Cap Brotherhood and save his robot-girl
